 <title>Excerpt 3 from ALL THE WAY</title>
 <link>https://kennedyprize.columbia.edu/winners/2013/schenkkan/media/excerpt-3-all-way</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;In this scene from Act Two of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;All the Way&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt; (from the bottom of page 99 to the bottom of page 101), Hubert Humphrey, Martin Luther King, Jr. and Bob Moses dissent about President Johnson&#039;s decision about MDFP representation at the Democratic convention of 1964, as MLK is &quot;torn between his conscience and political necessity.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-file field-type-file field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;file&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;file-icon&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;application/pdf&quot; src=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; /&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://kennedyprize.columbia.edu/winners/2013/schenkkan/sites/default/files/All%20the%20Way%20-%20EMK%20Excerpt%203.pdf&quot; type=&quot;application/pdf; length=155235&quot;&gt;All the Way - EMK Excerpt 3.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-person field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/person/hubert-humphrey&quot;&gt;Hubert Humphrey&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/person/martin-luther-king-jr&quot;&gt;Martin Luther King Jr.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-subject field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/subject/history&quot;&gt;History&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/subject/playwriting&quot;&gt;Playwriting&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-media-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/media-type/document&quot;&gt;Document