 <title>Hubert Humphrey and Martin Luther King, Jr.</title>
 <link>https://kennedyprize.columbia.edu/winners/2013/schenkkan/media/hubert-humphrey-and-martin-luther-king-jr</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hubert Humphrey and Martin Luther King, Jr.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://kennedyprize.columbia.edu/winners/2013/schenkkan/sites/default/files/Hubert_Humphrey_and_Martin_Luther_King_NYWTS.jpg&quot; width=&quot;3000&quot; height=&quot;2395&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-person field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/person/hubert-humphrey&quot;&gt;Hubert Humphrey&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/person/martin-luther-king-jr&quot;&gt;Martin Luther King Jr.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-subject field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/subject/history&quot;&gt;History&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-media-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/media-type/image&quot;&gt;Image&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-content-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/content-type/photo&quot;&gt;Photo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot